Johannesburg- Somizi Mhlongo has come to the rescue for those who do not have valentines dates this coming valentines day. The former Idols SA judge will be offering a date at certain prices to his adoring fans. The cost for a valentines date with Somizi is made up of different packages which ranges from R2 000 for a “high five” to R70 000 for two hours of Somizi’s time and company, with a bonus of a goodbye kiss to end the date. Somizi took to social media to share the costs of his services to those who will need them on the 14th of February. “I’m taking bookings for valentine’s day for those that don’t have dates not that I don’t have any valentine’s mine starts at 8 pm so I’m available before 8,” he wrote.  For the latest entertainment news from Sunday World, click here. Or read the latest from Shwashwi here. Follow @SundayWorldZA on Twitter and @sundayworldza on Instagram, or like our Facebook Page, Sunday World, by clicking here for the latest breaking news in South Africa. To Subscribe to Sunday World, click here.